Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.03,0:00:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let go now!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.61,0:00:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Regrouped in the air?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun has...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,become a bird!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.99,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that? \NTop six. Or else...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The club will be disbanded!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Demon...!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.57,0:02:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking the high bar from us wasn't enough?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.47,0:02:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That old hag acts like the women's club deserves everything under the sun!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.41,0:02:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something, \Nthree little dolts?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Three dolts?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.03,0:02:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The "Three Dolts" special program \Nin the stream of embarrassment—isn't it about you? {piling shame on top of shame - not sure what she's talking about, sounds a lot like some reference}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.69,0:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That hag...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.44,0:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll never stop making fun of us!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all part of her scheme.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.16,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it was decided by the board of directors, \Nthere won't be taking it back.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do it, somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.20,0:02:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, how many points do we need to score to place 6th in the district?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.26,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Let me think, who made it to the top six in the last tournament...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gyotoku Middle School.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Gyotoku Middle School placed 6th with 79 points.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.07,0:03:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, how do you know this?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you underestimate me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re full of surprises.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.05,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In team competitions, the scores of the top three members of the team are totaled for each event.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.16,0:03:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you score the maximum 10 points in each event, then the total for the three events will be 90 points.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.34,0:03:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gyotoku School at 6th place had 79 points \Nacross three events.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.54,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Divided by 9 for 3 people, \Nthe average is about 8.8 per person.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.78,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What did our team score last time?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.15,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,55 points.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.62,0:03:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,55 divided by 9... That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,About 6.1 per person.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.09,0:03:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? So we're just a few points short of 8.8?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most difficult part.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.90,0:04:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait a minute, last time I got 8.5 on the floor, \N7.5 on the high bar, and 8.5 in vaulting.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.17,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is our average score still so low?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so that's what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.72,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of Fujidiot, Uchidiot, and Sanadiot \Ndragging us down?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump us together!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.37,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to get our performance called off for lack of members!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.00,0:04:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why Fujidiot had to perform too!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, but my points were cut off...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.91,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,First off, it was my zero points that got cut off.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.08,0:04:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you way below the Captain in score yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't even worth mentioning!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.26,0:04:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One way or another, we've got to boost our average from 6.1 to over 8.8!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that is the main problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are so dense.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.54,0:05:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to score 6th, right? \NThen we can find a way to do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you'll need to break a sweat for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.64,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do our best!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With Ultra Ganba!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.13,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to hear. \NWell then, shall we try it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.07,0:05:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Ultra Ganba Part 2!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.25,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your first priority should be mastering more difficult techniques.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.39,0:05:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, your routines have mostly consisted of basic techniques.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.14,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you perfect those, \Nthey won’t score many points.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking for too much. \NIf it was just the bar, we could get by,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.36,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but there are two other events as well!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.47,0:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that. Therefore, each of you will master one special technique that'll amaze the judges
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.34,0:05:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in an event you're good at, \Naiming for a personal score of 9.2 or higher.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,9.2 in each event?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.28,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Glasses, you're good at vaulting, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.71,0:06:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have you perform \Na double front somersault.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.72,0:06:04.23,Top,,0,0,0,,Double front somersault...?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.70,0:06:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You, the Muscle. You prefer techniques that allow you to show off your strength, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll perform the straight-arm, straight-body handstand. {伸身伸腕プレス倒立 - had to drop "press" for CPS}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.74,0:06:17.17,Top,,0,0,0,,Straight-arm, straight-body handstand!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.97,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight-arm, straight-body handstand {伸身伸腕プレス倒立}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Wait a minute, \NI'm the prince of floor here!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.61,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a Jaeger \Nthat's worth a 30-carat diamond.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,Diamond?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,Diamond, all right!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What a Flathead! {simple-minded; one-track-minded​}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what about me?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.20,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You already have an average \Nabove 8 points, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.40,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need to do is polish whatever you're doing now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.10,0:06:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.86,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got two months until the tournament
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.04,0:06:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Spend the first month \Nlearning more difficult techniques.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.07,0:07:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then spend the remaining month perfecting the execution. All right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam, isn't there something I could do?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to keep doing what you usually do,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll be all set.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.38,0:07:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, only up to four members can perform.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to us and relax!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,Performing as usual?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.99,0:07:22.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,I know I'm not a full-fledged member yet, \Nbut I feel overlooked. {/regular}{(feeling) impatient; irritated}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.61,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Shun-kun, you can do backflips so easily?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If only a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.85,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a backflip that smooth is amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! I'll go first!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way! {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.11,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... Are you stupid? \NMy technique needs to be polished first!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.89,0:07:48.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,I see. Fujimaki's presence alone motivates everyone, pushing us to aim for a better team score.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.03,Thought,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Madam?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course it worked like a charm.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, Eri, who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.61,0:08:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're reviewing materials and brainstorming new supreme techniques. {hissatsuwaza = killer technique = something that'll hit the nail's head, idk what else to choose here}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.08,0:08:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to seeing the results in two months!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Supreme technique...?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.33,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be really helpful \Nif I learned something new too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, take your seats, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.01,0:08:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sagara Mariko, our new transfer student.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Treat her well, will you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sit over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.96,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Her uniform is a sailor suit.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sagara-san, did you choose a club already?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.15,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At our school, you have to enroll \Nin some athletic club.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet... \NI'm in a pickle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the volleyball club?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.66,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it when you launch off the high bar at this angle...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah... This book...!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about the bar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I need it for a moment!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this book?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.17,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's not here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you exercising on the high bar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? High bar?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.12,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we do. \NWe're in the gymnastics club.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gymnastics club?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.67,0:10:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... If it's not too much of a bother, \Ncould you teach me how to do a back hip circle?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.14,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Back hip circle?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.90,0:10:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Run up... \NRun up and... Jump! {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.92,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Run up! \NRun up and... Jump!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you! {nc}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha so relaxed about? \NWhat a jerk!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.29,0:10:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everyone, take a tea break!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.26,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush. \NPushing yourself too hard won't do you any good. {to strain (oneself); to bear down; to exert oneself}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.31,0:10:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimaki, you come here too!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that guy doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a back hip circle?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.54,0:11:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not too much of a bother, \Ncould you teach me how to do a back hip circle?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.09,0:11:06.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,Sagara Mariko... \NWhat an odd girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.82,0:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, back at my previous school, \Nthey nicknamed me "Turtle." {kanman = slow; sluggish; dull; slack; inactive}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Turtle?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to say that I'm sluggish. {slow; sluggish; inert}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.44,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, at the elementary \Nschool, I was "Flatfish." {medium-fatty tuna}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that—Miss Slow. {unsure it's miss, maybe some Japanese word but I can't get it}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.46,0:11:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There were also "Li'l Mariko, Lame Duck, \NHelpless Girl," et cetera. {marude dameko = completely useless/good for nothing}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst one was probably "Potato." {hechima = loofah/worthless thing}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they meant by that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.60,0:11:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's quite an impressive list. \NDid you really change schools that many times?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.72,0:11:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a wandering transfer girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.17,0:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing I noticed is that those nicknames always came after gym class.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand \Nwhat this means, Fujimaki-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.45,0:12:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I'm just hopeless \Nwhen it comes to sports.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why I must teach you \Nthe back hip circle?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't even do this, \NI'll be at a loss during the class.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.43,0:12:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably feel embarrassed.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic, even.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.50,0:12:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.00,0:12:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, it's okay if you don't wanna...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.67,0:12:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.00,0:12:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly how you feel! \NI really do!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.72,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.52,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In truth, I'm not good at sports either.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.96,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how it feels to be rejected by a place! {unable to stay (on); unable to endure being somewhere a second longer; feel like running away}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.46,0:12:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected by a place? \NAh... I'm not sure you do understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you mustn't run away!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Changing schools won't solve anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to face challenges head-on!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I transferred because of my dad's job, though...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll be fine. \NTrust me, I’ll make sure of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.48,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.05,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start—this is overhand grip.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the underhand grip.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use whichever is easier for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it at shoulder-width.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.99,0:13:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As you pull your belly up to the bar, \Nsharply kick your legs.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're good!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.15,0:13:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I also couldn't do the back hip circle \Nuntil I joined the gymnastics club.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But then it came naturally to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.01,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, I realized the main point: whatever you do, do it with confidence. {/you need confidence that you can do it}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now you give it a shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.85,0:13:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'll probably try on this one first. It's lower.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.08,0:13:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise not to laugh.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.40,0:13:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess I'm a lost cause, after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Once more!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.98,0:14:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see them? {/panties}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.90,0:14:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wear your gym clothes next time, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.34,Thought,,0,0,0,,This'll be harder than I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.78,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, impressive!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they really in middle school?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.18,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heisei gymnastics club is one of a kind.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No, you see...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the women's team of it is outstanding.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.30,0:14:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But the men's team is going \Nto get really great really soon too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha talking about? {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.30,0:14:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hanging out with a girl? \NThat's new.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.28,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you see... She's a transfer student and she wanted to know what our gymnastics club is like.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Sagara Mariko.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.12,0:14:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise not to interfere with your practice, \Nso can we take just a quick tour?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.68,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, sure... Be our guest!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.83,0:15:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get to know her, Sagara-san is nothing like how she seems at first.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sailor uniform, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.81,0:15:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pft. She's but a brat, \Ncompared to our Reiko-sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.64,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Start practicing!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.15,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold me tight, dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These muscles are quite something!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.37,0:15:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Higashi-senpai \Nis the club's muscle... {no clue what's kitte, could be "should've gone to body building club instead"}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.38,0:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going, Sagara-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.25,0:15:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Fujimaki-kun, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Those push-ups look weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.59,0:16:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because Higashi-senpai needs strength training for the new technique
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.59,0:16:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll use in the upcoming tournament.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.66,0:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks difficult...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.01,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, they're so hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell you ticking me for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's overdoing it. {no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.19,0:17:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those who can't jump even in the in the gymnastics club! He's just like me! {fr fr}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that wasn't very nice of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.91,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know, the vaulting is actually my specialty.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.27,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you jump, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.27,0:17:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was mental training. {/imaginary }
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.54,0:17:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When you become a true specialist like me, \Nyou'll also place great emphasis on mental training.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.71,0:17:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.68,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In the upcoming tournament, \NI must achieve the highest score in vaulting.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working on a secret plan for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.89,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's important here \Nis the rhythm when you jump.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.59,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The rhythm for kicking the springboard, \Nlaunching, and landing
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.16,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,needs to change from the usual "ton-ton-ton" to "to-to-ton!"
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? In other words, I need to...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? She left!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.61,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so... So...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.91,0:18:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So disrespectful!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lady!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Up here!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.65,0:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing up there?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.15,0:18:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm contemplating the future of our club.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.79,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The future of this club truly hinges on the upcoming tournament.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.10,0:18:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is working hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.44,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... It sounds like you're having a tough time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we'll manage.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.34,0:18:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, there's me—the Prince of Floor with a diamond Jaeger, Sanada Toshihiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Where are you going? Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujimaki-kun, gymnastics club looks fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.47,0:18:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to choose something, \NI think I'll join the gymnastics club.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? are you serious, Sagara-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.88,0:18:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll introduce you to Reiko-senpai.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.53,0:18:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Wait, Fujimaki-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.49,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, Fujimaki! \NWhat am I supposed to do now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiko-senpai!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Shun-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,"Shun-kun?"
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.11,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl wants to join the gymnastics club.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.12,0:19:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiko-senpai is an Olympic team candidate.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.06,0:19:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, Shun-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.66,0:19:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you train with Reiko-senpai, \Nyou'll definitely improve.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.79,0:19:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She never forgets the important points!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.09,0:19:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, even I got better in no time!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shun-kun, that's enough promoting me for now.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.70,0:19:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Orikasa, the third-year. \NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you around. \NThe women's club is this way.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.48,0:19:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you daydreaming here? \NWho's gonna support me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your care is wasted on her! \NShe'll quit in three days! {overly helpful person; annoyingly helpful person}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.92,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.55,0:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see her putting up with the rigorous training of our women's club either.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't last more than a day here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.36,0:20:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Reiko-senpai is a very kind mentor, \Nso she'll totally be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! Even Reiko-sama's help won't be enough. {unsure}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Come on, we gotta work!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.90,0:20:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to join \Nthe gymnastics club?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you're good at?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.44,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the women's gymnastics club \Nthat I want to join.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.02,0:20:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The club I want to join \Nis the men's gymnastics club!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.48,0:20:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sagara-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.41,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying, Sagara-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How can a girl do that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for wasting your time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.33,0:20:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna join the men's gymnastics club!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Sagara-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I’m sorry, Reiko-senpai!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.71,0:20:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what Fujimaki-kun's type is like?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.18,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe even "a day" was too optimistic of a prediction.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,He's fawning on her so much! {not sure}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.26,0:21:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see them? Did you?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.73,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a better fit for the men's club. {than for women's}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.22,0:21:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of me! \NI'll do my best!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.88,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can make it work. {unsure what he means}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.90,0:21:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.88,0:21:30.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A female member in the men's gymnastics club? Are you sure that'll work out well?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.45,0:21:34.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But if it lifts everyone's spirits, \Nwell, that's not such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.32,0:21:38.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The summer tournament is fast approaching!  \NYou all worked hard to secure 6th place!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go strong on your path to the gold medal, \NGanbarist Shun!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.70,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it again...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.42,0:23:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do in just one month?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.06,0:23:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.00,0:23:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no longer our Captain?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.37,0:23:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told you about the gold medal,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.67,0:23:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't laugh, but instead said that if I dream big, I must work hard for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.63,0:23:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell me to dream big?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! I beg you not to quit!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.71,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me alone already!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.00,0:23:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Ganba: No Way! \NCaptain Quits the Club. {嘘だ!キャプテンの退部届}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:45.01,0:23:51.00,NarratorTop,,0,0,0,,Thomas flair is performed on top of a 110-cm tall pommel horse with your legs apart.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.00,0:23:53.36,NarratorTop,,0,0,0,,And when you do it with your feet together, it's called circle. {両足旋回 - no idea what to call it in EN}
